Directory names are based on https://tools.ietf.org/html/bcp47

This also allows languages like: Welsh/Kymrisch or Frisian

locale examples: en, en-US, nl, nl-NL
	2*3ALPHA            ; shortest ISO 639 code
	["-" extlang]       ; sometimes followed by extended language subtags

